Bitfield value of step voltage transition value

uint16_t pmhalTps65218RegulatorProp::stepVoltTransition

Transition step voltage in mV. Voltage at which step voltage changes from stepVoltLow to stepVoltHigh.

The regulator type namely PMHAL_TPS65218_RTYPE_DCDC or PMHAL_TPS65218_RTYPE_LDO.
